    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54B32 atmospheric inline-six. This engine features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, providing crisp throttle response and a broad power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Key preventative maintenance is addressed: the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates, and the VANOS hub and solenoid have been overhauled. The suspension utilizes upgraded bushings and monotube dampers for improved damping rates. While the paint exhibits minor road rash consistent with enthusiast use, the mechanical integrity and kinematic feedback are exceptional for this high-performance chassis.",
